        builder.add_edge("excel_handler", END)

    ADD:
        builder.add_conditional_edges(
            "excel_handler",
            excel_handler_post_router,
            {
                "auto_submit": "submit_mrr",
                "end": END,
            }
        )

    Also (if registered separately): the "excel_handler_node" name.

